text: Michael Cuneo is an electrical engineer at the Sandia National Laboratories in Albuquerque, New Mexico. Cuneo was named a Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2014 for his contributions to inertial confinement fusion with magnetically-driven implosions and electrode cleaning. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:Sandia National Laboratories people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
